Author: fragilemndstrongmind
Text: And don't want to constantly think about food, enjoy things other than food / exercise, actually have the motivation and energy to do something besides run, cook, eat...  Currently always want to eat, never feel like I need to eat, hungrier right after a meal than after 15 hours not eating and a long run? "Eat to live, don't live to eat" I am literally doing the latter, like everything I do is based around food and runners high.
